title: European analysts see the U.S. midterm results as reassuring for Ukraine and NATO.
dc:creator: Steven Erlanger and Alexandra Stevenson

media:content.media:credit: T.J. Kirkpatrick for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: The U.S. Capitol in Washington on Wednesday, the morning after Election Day. Diplomats and analysts are considering how the midterm elections will affect support for Ukraine and NATO.
